QSqPjA8Tx8dFisjZNeptdEjq8HuJqkA\" data-hovercard=\"\/ajax\/hovercard\/user.php?id=1348004796&amp;extragetparams=%7B%22__tn__%22%3A%22%2CdK-R-R%22%2C%22eid%22%3A%22ARCOH4UPkMYdGwq4k8iaUAigDU9BgwSG3OTjiOz4s3PzIElwD-ulkgKocWWCNLT_OMQetL1QdG3yNCR9%22%2C%22fref%22%3A%22mentions%22%7D\" data-hovercard-prefer-more-content-show=\"1\">Tanya Aldave<\/a>\u00a0who organized the fundraiser. Here is a thank you note from the church:<\/p>\n<p>&#8220;We are very grateful to United Help Ukraine for its help in this difficult time for our country. For two years now we had no heating in our church, which is located near the front line in the Donetsk region.<br \/>\nWe did not have the means necessary to buy suc<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">h an expensive and modern equipment.<br \/>\nHere, in the place near the war zone, we serve different groups of people, but most importantly, we serve children of all ages. That&#8217;s why we had to find a way to heat the church, and now the problem is solved and it&#8217;s warm here.<br \/>\nYou would not imagine how important for us is this heating system: now we can better serve the people. This was done thanks to you, United Help Ukraine. May the Lord bless you and help you in all you do.&#8221;<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>United Help Ukraine is grateful to our donors who contributed to buy the heating system for a church near the war zone. Special thanks to\u00a0Tanya Aldave\u00a0who organized the fundraiser. Here is a thank you note from the church: &#8220;We are very grateful to United Help Ukraine for its help in this difficult time for our<a href=\"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/archives\/3969\">[&#8230;]<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":18,"featured_media":3970,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[2,8],"tags":[22,79,92,70],"wppr_data":{"cwp_meta_box_check":"No"},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/w